# API Integration

- All API calls must use types from src/core/types.rs contracts - match backend exactly
- Use fetch API or axios for HTTP requests - prefer fetch for simplicity
- Handle errors explicitly - never swallow API errors
- Use async/await for async operations - avoid promise chains
- Type all API responses - use TypeScript interfaces matching backend types
- Implement proper error handling - handle network errors, 4xx, 5xx responses
- Use OpenAPI schema as source of truth - regenerate types when schema changes
- Keep API client in dedicated api/ directory - separate from UI components
- Use environment variables for API base URL - VITE_API_URL or similar
- Implement request/response interceptors for auth/error handling if needed
